{"tid":1840943,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"叫我黑醫黑護囉，我係都唔救你班藍絲黑警，我call sick","createTime":"2020-01-25T05:25:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T11:31:05.000Z","uid":264535,"like":149,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"e02912facd367f50eb90ead373607a62a7b39a5b","tid":1840943,"uid":264535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T05:25:01.000Z","msg":"我一定會拒絕醫所有警察及直系家屬。咁愛國？返大陸醫啦你老母，你嘅祖國隱瞞疫情，搞到隻病毒爆得幾撚勁。深圳醫療咁撚勁，返去放催淚彈殺菌囉。<br />\n<br />\n屌你老味，示威抗爭嘅時候拒絕人道救援，打到啲細路頭破血流。<br />\n<br />\n我睇吓你啲槍炮勁定病毒勁？睇吓你啲大話有用定專業醫療知識有用。"},{"pid":"f6d5daa1f5e887f2bfacff9fcc16453a6953f675","tid":1840943,"uid":126621,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T05:25:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>政府不封關不作為<br />\n讓武漢病毒入侵香港<br />\n病毒持有者唔發燒，過關體檢check唔到<br />\n唔封關根本係謀殺香港人<br />\n<br />\n醫護界作為唯一能議價的人<br />\n卻認為罷工乜乜乜，責任攬上自己到<br />\n醫護不作為如同站在政府的一方<br />\n真係枉為人，我呸。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">下面兩條片講病毒唔會發燒，過幾日就死</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/5l7bf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2F5l7bf&d=EXOoM7fQMXhTNR4rfnaZT0pSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=68729f21\" target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/5l7bf</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/t7d44\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Ft7d44&d=EXOoM7fQMXhTNR4rfnaZT0pSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=169ad08c\" target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/t7d44</a><br />\n<br />\n呢條片係專家分析<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有兩種冠狀病毒</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://fbwat.ch/1aeLVmnDo4lRHvIc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffbwat.ch%2F1aeLVmnDo4lRHvIc&d=EXOoM7fQMXhTNR4rfnaZT0pSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=e3ebf142\" target=\"_blank\">https://fbwat.ch/1aeLVmnDo4lRHvIc</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yYS7rf7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyYS7rf7.png&h=fa7cecd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: 